<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_307_r1l17"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_307_r1l16">VVir </ab></add> ſchıcken cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> dıſen <expan>gegenvvertige<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_307_r1l18"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Smyd<ex>en</ex></expan> mit xv . ſtück vveins . vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_307_r1l19">daʒ Jr vns <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vveine <expan>günne<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet bey euch in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_307_r1l20">Stat nydercʒulegen vnd Jm einen cʒu ſchicken der Jm darcʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_307_r1l21">hılfflich vnd fürderlich ſey / Daran beweiſt Jr vns <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_307_r1l22">lıeb vnd <expan>freuntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> . vnd vvaʒ auch der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> diener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_307_r1l23">darümb cʒu diſem mal an euch werb . des wöllet Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_307_r1l24"><expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd darynne <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> tun Als etc Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_307" id="152v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Eger</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, <add>wir</add> schicken czu
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> disen
                            <expan>gegenwertige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Smyd<ex>en</ex></expan> mit xv stück weins, und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir uns
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> weine <expan>günne<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wöllet bey euch in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> stat nyderczulegen und im
                        einen czu schicken, der im darczu hilfflich und fürderlich sey, daran
                        beweist ir uns <expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan> lieb und
                                <expan>freunts<ex>chaft</ex></expan>. Und waz auch der
                                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener darümb czu disem mal an euch werb, des
                        wöllet im <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und darynne
                            <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> tun. Als etc. Das
                            <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
